commit.message:
* Login operation does not require a true/false parameter as it automatically implies that login operation is required.
* Cosmetic changes to the help file.

* Error messages are 1 error are now grouped in one line
* Readded sanitize_auto_delete_delay
Logs can be enabled/disabled via the config file.

* Making use of the configuration file
* Removed popup notifications as they do not make any sense to have in 
the first place
* Code simplification
